snippet.title: The Settlers 2 gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for The Settlers 2 (aka settlers ii, the: veni, vidi, vici), Dos PC game produced by Blue Byte in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/the-settlers-ii/1669/
Playing a basic Roman campaign and then starting a World campaign.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:

Worms: Reinforcements - https://youtu.be/2fK2SqebbPg
X-COM: Apocalypse - https://youtu.be/bo4XKV3F9Hg
